	<hr />

	<h2>Font Size</h2>

	<p>
		Astro UXDS font size tokens define the font size of text styles and
		elements. The design tokens are based on a t-shirt sizing system where the <code
			>font-size-base</code
		> token equals 1 rem (16 px by default), and font sizes are either smaller (sm,
		xs) or larger (lg, xl, 2xl, 3xl, 4xl, 5xl, 6xl) than the base. For reference,
		the P body text style uses the <code>font-size-base</code>
		token to set the font size.
	</p>
	{
		reference('dark', 'fontSizes').map((token) => (
			<rux-design-token-preview
				name={token.name}
				value={token.value}
				alias={token.referenceToken}
